	ItemType "Amazon Bows" "Amazon Javelins" "Amazon Spears" "Auric Shields" "Axes" "Belts" "Blunt Weapons" "Body Armors" "Boots" "Bows" "Cloaks" "Clubs" "Crossbow" "Gloves" "Hammers" "Hand to Hand" "Helmets" "Javelins" "Knives" "Maces" "One Handed Weapons" "Orbs" "Pelts" "Polearms" "Primal Helmets" "Scepters" "Shields" "Spears" "Staves" "Throwing Axes" "Throwing Knives" "Two Handed Weapons" "Voodoo Heads" "Wands"
	Rarity == "Normal"
	Tier <= "Exceptional"
	ItemLevel > 74

Hide #High bases "elite bases" - After ilvl 74 exceptional magic rarity items will no longer show, only higher bases will appear
	ItemType "Amazon Bows" "Amazon Javelins" "Amazon Spears" "Auric Shields" "Axes" "Belts" "Blunt Weapons" "Body Armors" "Boots" "Bows" "Cloaks" "Clubs" "Crossbow" "Gloves" "Hammers" "Hand to Hand" "Helmets" "Javelins" "Knives" "Maces" "One Handed Weapons" "Orbs" "Pelts" "Polearms" "Primal Helmets" "Scepters" "Shields" "Spears" "Staves" "Throwing Axes" "Throwing Knives" "Two Handed Weapons" "Voodoo Heads" "Wands"
